text: @UPSHelp Hi, I never received one of my packages. There was a open claim on it and it was said to be stolen. I was supposed to provide a police report to be able to get the refund but I have no way to get a police report and now I lost the 55$ I spent.
@sunshinexukun I would then recommend that you stay in contact with your shipper to see if they would be willing to provide an alternate solution. ^KD
